Building OpenAMQ

Building on Posix
-----------------

Prerequisites:

    1. gcc

Step 1: define these environment variables (example values).

IBASE=$HOME
INCDIR=$IBASE/include
LIBDIR=$IBASE/lib
PATH=$HOME/bin:...

Step 2: unpackage the sources:

    unzip -a openamq-X.YxN-src

Step 3: build and install

    cd openamq-X.YxN
    sh build.sh

Step 4: run in openamq-X.YxN\openamq

    cd openamq
    amqpsrv


Building on Windows 2000, XP
----------------------------

Prerequisites:

    1. MSVC 6.x or higher, installed for command-line use
    2. InfoZip 'unzip'

Step 1: define these environment variables (example values).

CCDIR=C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio\VC98
CCOPTS= /I"%INCDIR%" /I"%CCDIR%\include"
IBASE=c:\imatix
INCDIR=c:\imatix\include
LIBDIR=c:\imatix\lib
PATH=c:\imatix\bin;%CCDIR%\bin;...

Step 2: unpackage the sources:

    unzip -a openamq-X.YxN-src

Step 3: build and install

    cd openamq-X.YxN
    cd base
    build
    cd ..\base2
    build
    cd ..\openamq
    build

Step 4: run in openamq-X.YxN\openamq

    amqpsrv

    
